=== Simple Swallow
--- input
\if(true):>
foo
--- rawast
+RCALL
  =SYMREF <intrinsic>.if
  >ARG condition
  +AST
    =LIT text "true"
  -AST
  >ARG then
  +AST
    =LIT text "foo"
  -AST
  >ARG else
  =VOID
-RCALL
--- expr
+BRANCHES
  =ENUM Boolean "true"
  >BRANCH 0
  =VOID
  >BRANCH 1
  =TEXT literal "foo"
-BRANCHES
--- document
=RAW Raw "foo"